snippet.title: Nintendo Switch 「QV」 | Official Accolades Trailer
snippet.description:
As Dimensional Core stopped working, unbalanced dimensions are on the brink of collapse!
Join Quby and her companions from other worlds on their quest to save the dimensions!
Check out what the critics say about the Nintendo Switch action adventure 「QV」!

▶Nintendo eShop : https://store.nintendo.co.kr/70010000032520
▶Official 「QV」 Twitter : https://twitter.com/QV_NEWS
